;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252F1-100-faster-decay%252Fid210986853%253Fi%253D210987115%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Decay Music-Michael Nyman']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/broadcasting-from-home.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/broadcast.jpg" alt="Broadcasting from Home / Penguin Cafe Orchestra" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/broadcasting-from-home.php">Broadcasting from Home<br />Penguin Cafe Orchestra</a></h4><p>【WET】ペンギン・カフェのアルバムの中でも、特に美しい曲が揃っているアルバム。雨の日を穏やかに彩ってくれる極上の音楽。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001AI93QS?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001AI93QS" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Broadcasting from Home-Penguin Cafe Orchestra']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmusic-for-a-found-harmonium%252Fid283824929%253Fi%253D283824974%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%25" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Broadcasting from Home-Penguin Cafe Orchestra']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/04/endless-summer.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/endlesssummer.jpg" alt="Endless Summer / Fennesz" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/04/endless-summer.php">Endless Summer<br />Fennesz</a></h4><p>【WET】ノイズが美しいメロディーを奏でるエレクトロニカの名盤。雨音と電子ノイズが一体化して、奇跡的に美しい空間が現れます。</p><div class="buy"