K9" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Tehillim-Steve Reich']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Ftehillim-parts-1-2%252Fid213632726%253Fi%253D213632729%2526uo%253D6%2526partnerId%253D30 ARTI" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Tehillim-Steve Reich']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/ege-bamyasi.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/egebamyasi.jpg" alt="Ege Bamyasi / Can" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/ege-bamyasi.php">Ege Bamyasi<br />Can</a></h4><p>【DRY】ダモ鈴木が在籍していた時期のカンの作品は傑作揃いだが、その中でもアヴァンギャルドながらポップな印象のあるアルバム。狂おしい雨の日に。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0011WMHRA?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0011WMHRA" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Ege Bamyasi-Can']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=" ARTISTNAME: Can" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Ege Bamyasi-Can']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/reggae-anthology-music-is-the-rod.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/reggaeantho.jpg" alt="Reggae Anthology: Music Is the Rod / Garnet Silk" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/05/reggae-anthology-music-is-the-rod.php">Reggae Anthology: Music Is the Rod<br />Garnet Silk</a></h4><p>【DRY】ガーネット・シルクのコンピレーションは数多いが、代表曲がほぼ網羅されているという点でこれを。瞬時に晴天に連れて行かれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="